import { Accordion, Card } from 'react-bootstrap';
export default function Footer() {
  return (
    <Accordion defaultActiveKey="0">
      <Card>
        <Accordion.Toggle
          onClick={console.log(1)}
          as={Card.Header}
          eventKey="0"
        >
          Click me!
        </Accordion.Toggle>
        <Accordion.Collapse eventKey="0">
          <Card.Body>Hello! m the body</Card.Body>
        </Accordion.Collapse>
      </Card>
      <Card>
        <Accordion.Toggle as={Card.Header} eventKey="1">
          Click me!
        </Accordion.Toggle>
        <Accordion.Collapse eventKey="1">
          <Card.Body>Hello! m another body</Card.Body>
        </Accordion.Collapse>
      </Card>
    </Accordion>
  );
}
